Settings description
__________________________________________________________________

 * |OVP_DocBegin_BoxAlgorithm_MultipleChoiceTest_Settings|
 * |OVP_DocEnd_BoxAlgorithm_MultipleChoiceTest_Settings|

 * |OVP_DocBegin_BoxAlgorithm_MultipleChoiceTest_Setting1|
This is the gtk builder interface to use for the GUI.
 * |OVP_DocEnd_BoxAlgorithm_MultipleChoiceTest_Setting1|

 * |OVP_DocBegin_BoxAlgorithm_MultipleChoiceTest_Setting2|
This is the XML file name where all questions and answers configuration are defined.
 * |OVP_DocEnd_BoxAlgorithm_MultipleChoiceTest_Setting2|

 * |OVP_DocBegin_BoxAlgorithm_MultipleChoiceTest_Setting3|
This is the file name where all selected answers are saved.
 * |OVP_DocEnd_BoxAlgorithm_MultipleChoiceTest_Setting3|

 * |OVP_DocBegin_BoxAlgorithm_MultipleChoiceTest_Setting4|
This stimulation is used as a basis for the answers flashes. For example, flashing the first answer consists in sending this
exact stimulation code to the first input. Flashing the second answer needs this stimulation code + 1 and so on.
 * |OVP_DocEnd_BoxAlgorithm_MultipleChoiceTest_Setting4|

 * |OVP_DocBegin_BoxAlgorithm_MultipleChoiceTest_Setting5|
This stimulation is used as a basis for the validating flashes. For example, flashing the retry button consists in sending this
exact stimulation code to the second input. Flashing the validate button needs this stimulation code + 1.
 * |OVP_DocEnd_BoxAlgorithm_MultipleChoiceTest_Setting5|

  * |OVP_DocBegin_BoxAlgorithm_MultipleChoiceTest_Setting6|
This stimulation is used as a basis for the timer. For example, set the timer to 0 consists in sending this
exact stimulation code to the fifth input. Set the timer to 1 needs this stimulation code + 1 and so on.
* |OVP_DocEnd_BoxAlgorithm_MultipleChoiceTest_Setting6|

* |OVP_DocBegin_BoxAlgorithm_MultipleChoiceTest_Setting7|
This stimulation defines the stimulation send when the selection received correspond
to an existing answer or to the validate button, according to the step.
* |OVP_DocEnd_BoxAlgorithm_MultipleChoiceTest_Setting7|

* |OVP_DocBegin_BoxAlgorithm_MultipleChoiceTest_Setting8|
This stimulation defines the stimulation send when the selection received not correspond
to an existing answer or to the validate button, according to the step.
* |OVP_DocEnd_BoxAlgorithm_MultipleChoiceTest_Setting8|

* |OVP_DocBegin_BoxAlgorithm_MultipleChoiceTest_Setting9|
This setting defines the language of the Quiz window.
This choice has no effect on the text defines in the question XML file.
* |OVP_DocEnd_BoxAlgorithm_MultipleChoiceTest_Setting9|

* |OVP_DocBegin_BoxAlgorithm_MultipleChoiceTest_Setting10|
This value is used to know the maximum of answers used for one question.
* |OVP_DocEnd_BoxAlgorithm_MultipleChoiceTest_Setting10| 

